GG Manager — Texnik topshiriq (Commercial v1)
Product nomi

GG Manager
to‘liq nomi: Geeks Game Club Manager

1. Loyiha maqsadi

GG Manager — bu lokal LAN asosida ishlovchi, 40–100 ta Windows gaming PC uchun professional game club boshqaruv platformasi.

Tizimning vazifasi:

club egasiga barcha kompyuterlar ustidan markazlashgan nazorat berish
mijozlarning sessiyalarini boshqarish
tarif, balans va kassani yuritish
client tomonda xavfsiz kiosk/shell muhit yaratish
mahsulotni boshqa game clublarga o‘rnatib, litsenziya asosida sotish imkonini berish
